createEquityConfig(address,bytes,uint256.details: Creates a new equity configuration contract and links it to the specified token.      Uses a proxy contract for upgradeability.      Can only be called by the owner.

params._data: Initialization data for the equity configuration.
params._token: Address of the token to be linked to the equity configuration.
params._totalTokenSupply: Total supply of the equity tokens.
params.mappingValue: Identifier for mapping the created equity configuration.

createFund(address,bytes,uint256,string).details: Creates a new fund contract and links it to the specified token.      Uses a proxy contract for upgradeability.      Can only be called by the owner.

params._token: Address of the token to be linked to the fund.
params._totalTokenSupply: Total supply of the fund tokens.
params.mappingValue: Identifier for mapping the created fund.

init(address).details: Initializes the contract with the given master factory address.      This function can only be called once due to the `initializer` modifier.

params._factory: Address of the master factory contract.

setAdminWallet(address,string).details: Updates the admin wallet address.      Can only be called by the owner.

params._actionID: Unique identifier for tracking the action.

setFee(address,uint16,uint16,uint16,uint.details: Sets various fee parameters for a given token.      The fee values must not exceed 20% (2000 basis points).      Once set, admin fees cannot be reset.      Can only be called by the owner.

params._dividendFee: Fee for dividend distributions (in basis points).
params._escrowFee: Fee for escrow transactions (in basis points).
params._redemptionFee: Fee for token redemptions (in basis points).
params._wrapFee: Fee for wrapping assets (in basis points).
params.actionID: Unique identifier for tracking the action.

setImpl(address,address).details: Sets the implementation addresses for Fund and Equity Configuration.      Can only be called by the owner.

params._implEquityConfig: Address of the Equity Configuration implementation contract.
params._implFund: Address of the Fund implementation contract.

setMasterFactory(address).details: Updates the master factory address.      Can only be called by the owner.
